    "narrative": "For today\u2019s slate, **Jackson Merrill** stands out as the clear cornerstone of the Austin Waves lineup. Boasting an elite efficiency score of 75.10, he benefits from a highly favorable matchup against Feltner, whose 4.63 xERA is the softest landing spot on our board. The combination of a 14% park boost and a massive 15% skill advantage against the starter makes him a high-ceiling anchor. While **Drake Baldwin** and **Luis Garc\u00eda Jr.** provide solid returns in the #2 hole\u2014both scoring well above the 55-point threshold\u2014the overall offensive strategy is anchored by **Jackson Merrill**\u2019s ability to capitalize on this specific pitching vulnerability.\n\nThe most difficult decision on today\u2019s bench was **Josh Jung**, who narrowly missed the cut with a score of 41.26. While **Josh Jung**\u2019s raw projection suggests he could produce, the optimizer favored **Marcell Ozuna** and **Luis Robert Jr.** due to their placement in the heart of the order and a slight advantage in their respective lineup roles, despite the tougher matchups against deGrom and Ryan. We are also monitoring **Luis Robert Jr.**, **Andy Pages**, and **Heliot Ramos** closely; while their scores are tempered by elite opposing arms and neutral platoon environments, their underlying speed metrics\u2014specifically the slow delivery of today\u2019s opposing pitchers\u2014provide a vital, albeit marginal, boost for our pursuit of stolen bases, which remains our highest priority.\n\nRisk management is paramount today, particularly with **Luis Robert Jr.**, **Andy Pages**, and **Marcell Ozuna** facing top-tier arms with xERAs near or below 3.30. We are essentially betting on talent over the environment for these roster spots. We continue to manage our daily game caps carefully, keeping the likes of **Gunnar Henderson** and **Vladimir Guerrero Jr.** inactive due to their off-day, while **Jordan Westburg** remains sidelined on the IL. Any volatility from the weather or last-minute lineup adjustments could force a pivot, but as currently structured, we are prioritizing high-leverage lineup slots to maximize our daily Roto accumulation.",
